<div class="vhs-page position-relative">
  <div class="vhs-page__grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="vhs-page__fog" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <section class="container py-5 vhs-hero">
    <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <span class="vhs-tag">Survival Horror</span>
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold vhs-title">VHS</h1>
        <p class="lead vhs-intro">Record. Reveal. Run.</p>
        <p class="vhs-copy">
          You awaken in a town that should be empty—yet something still moves in the static. With only an old VHS camcorder to
          guide you, you begin to see what your eyes cannot. Through the warped lens, hidden shapes emerge: ghosts, fragments,
          things that shouldn’t exist.
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-3 mt-4">
          <%= link_to 'Coming Soon on itch.io', 'https://itch.io', class: 'btn vhs-cta disabled', aria: { disabled: 'true' }, tabindex: '-1' %>
          <%= link_to 'View Gameplay Gallery', '#vhs-gallery', class: 'btn vhs-secondary' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 text-center">
        <div class="vhs-hero__frame mx-auto">
          <%= image_tag 'VHS_Banner.png', alt: 'VHS key art showing the haunted town skyline', class: 'img-fluid vhs-hero__image' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container pb-5 vhs-features">
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="vhs-feature-card h-100">
          <h2 class="h4">Analog Sight</h2>
          <p>Switch between reality and the camcorder&#39;s spectral feed to reveal routes, clues, and threats hidden in the fog.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="vhs-feature-card h-100">
          <h2 class="h4">Static-Torn Storytelling</h2>
          <p>Piece together tape fragments scattered across the town to uncover who—or what—warped this place beyond recognition.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="vhs-feature-card h-100">
          <h2 class="h4">Nerve-Shredding Atmosphere</h2>
          <p>Sound design and PSX-inspired visuals combine to deliver a Silent Hill homage filled with dread, grit, and analog warmth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="vhs-gallery" class="container pb-5 vhs-gallery">
    <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
      <div class="col-auto">
        <h2 class="h3 mb-0">Gameplay Glimpses</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-auto">
        <span class="vhs-gallery__note">Captured straight from the camcorder feed</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_1_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Player exploring a fog drenched street', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Static reveals the outline of something stalking the streets.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_4_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Camcorder view exposing ghostly silhouettes', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Switch realities to navigate impossible hallways and locked doors.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_6_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Encounter with a spectral entity emitting static', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Outrun specters that flicker in and out with each surge of interference.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_7_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Derelict alleyway lit by crimson emergency lights', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Environmental storytelling hints at the town&#39;s last broadcast.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_8_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Static drenched figure looming at the end of a corridor', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Keep moving—when the tape stops, the horrors step through.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_PS2.png', alt: 'Old television and VHS player setup in a dimly lit room', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Save progress by finding safe rooms equipped with analog relics.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container pb-5 vhs-lore">
    <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
        <div class="vhs-lore__frame">
          <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_2_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'VHS camcorder interface scanning a haunted plaza', class: 'img-fluid rounded-4' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
        <h2 class="h3">Stay Tuned</h2>
        <p>
          VHS is in active development, with new zones, haunt encounters, and analog puzzles being spooled up. Follow for updates
          as the town grows stranger and the signal grows stronger.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-0">
          Want to be the first to know when the download goes live? Keep an eye on itch.io and join the mailing list soon for
          exclusive beta access.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
